[SN]TITLE[SN]
European Taekwondo Championships: Olympic champion Jade Jones wins gold

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Great Britain's Olympic champion Jade Jones has won her first European Taekwondo Championships title.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
